LocationLastUpdatedSearchParameter

Parameter _lastUpdated:date

Searches based on the location lastUpdated field for the location record eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Location?_lastUpdated={date}

ResourceLocation
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesLocation
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
